This project includes a video showing how using the UART (USB) port you can communicate an arduino with a PC through an 
APP developed in C #



The operation is very simple

Step 1: Load the file located in the Arduino-project / ArduinoToPcSendAndRecibe.ino folder on your Arduino Uno / MEGA

Step 2: Run the Appl located in the folder Csharp / Debug /PCtoArduinoUSB.exe

The project is created with Visual Studio 2017 in c # language





If you want more information, you can contact me at electronicdinamicsystems@gmail.com
